headline: REGN Q1 Earnings Call: Pipeline Progress and EYLEA Headwinds Dominate Discussion
summary: Biotech company Regeneron (NASDAQ:REGN) missed Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q1 CY2025, with sales falling 3.7% year on year to $3.03 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $8.22 per share was 3% below analysts’ consensus estimates.
